I"Ì<p>Memory has <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/perception-is-context-dependent">top-down influences on the perceived reality</a>. It can be <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/incremental-writing-resembles-reactivation-and-reconsolidation">retrospectively modified</a>, and it can be seen as an <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/memory-is-perception-of-structural-artifacts">artifact</a>. In this, memory is like a manuscript.</p>
